# Authored on Windows, meant to run on Linux and macOS too. Normalise text in the
# repository and let each checkout use its own line endings.
* text=auto

# .sve savegames and .blend scenes are binary containers. Git must not go anywhere
# near their line endings: a "fixed" CRLF inside a savegame is a corrupt savegame.
*.sve binary
*.blend binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.pak binary
